<plot>A former mob hitman (Eric Roberts), now in witness protection, is forced to come out of retirement when his family is threatened by his cohorts. He teams up with a skateboarding kid (Esteban Powell), who has a computer disk that the mob wants to get their hands on that has a list of new names for individuals in the FBI witness protection program. The list includes his dad (Eric Poppick), who seperated from his mother years before and hadn't been seen since.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?241883</url></doc>
